
Epoch 3/10
176/176 [==============================] - 81s - loss: 1.3891 - acc: 0.5432 - val_loss: 1.3552 - val_acc: 0.5234
Epoch 4/10
176/176 [==============================] - 82s - loss: 1.3981 - acc: 0.5398 - val_loss: 1.3121 - val_acc: 0.5545
Epoch 5/10
176/176 [==============================] - 82s - loss: 1.4108 - acc: 0.5326 - val_loss: 1.2859 - val_acc: 0.5599
Epoch 6/10
176/176 [==============================] - 81s - loss: 1.3781 - acc: 0.5445 - val_loss: 1.3440 - val_acc: 0.5545
Epoch 7/10
176/176 [==============================] - 82s - loss: 1.3692 - acc: 0.5436 - val_loss: 1.2314 - val_acc: 0.5607
Epoch 8/10
176/176 [==============================] - 81s - loss: 1.3729 - acc: 0.5447 - val_loss: 1.2450 - val_acc: 0.5833
